Pseudo code for Rocks paper scissors

1. Define variables: Rock = r
					 Paper = p
					 Scissors = s

2. Player one (x) goes

3. At the same time, player 2 (y) goes

4. if 
	x = r && y = s ||
	x = p && y = r ||
    x = s && y = p 

    print "Player 1 wins!"


5. else if
	x = r && y = r ||
	x = p && y = p ||
	x = s && y = s

	print "It's a tie! Try again!"

6. else
	
	print "Player 2 wins!"

7. Repeat steps 1-6